    "(ii) AI Smartphones: AI smartphones (e.g., Apple Intelligence) enable cross-App data access and function calls by exposing App APIs to agents, better aligned with agent's strength in processing raw data than GUI emulation.",
    "(iii) MCP places large models at the core of the ecosystem, treating the entire Internet as its contextual knowledge base and toolkit.",
    "Standardized APIs, dynamic plugin support, and persistent context management allow a single model to orchestrate across diverse services.",
    "(iv) A2A protocol aims to form a decentralized agent network where agents autonomously discover, negotiate, and collaborate with each other.",
